title: Scunci Effortless Beauty Velour Comfy Twister, 3-Count, colors may vary
description: With scunci effortless beauty hair accessories a woman should never have a bad hair day. twisters are an essential for any woman with hair below chin length. keeps hair off the face while growing out or during sports. easily put hair up into a high ponytail or use low at the nape. wear one or mix for unique looks. good for quick casual style when you have to run out for errands. comfortable textural velour won't damage hair.

title: NYX Eyebrow Cake Powder, Black/Gray
description: Our recipe for cooking up exquisite eyebrows includes wax, tools and a pair of complementary powders, black and gray, which can be customized to create the ideal shade. Each eyebrow cake powder kit includes a slanted brush and a round wand to shape, style and tame eyebrows.

title: NYX Auto Eyebrow Pencil, Black
description: Create flawless arches with this eyebrow pencil, a blend of vegetable, coconut and soy bean oil that guarantees a fluid application and sensational color. Use the built-in brush to blend color and style your eyebrows to perfection. Available in 8 shades.
